code: @Override protected JndiRegistry createRegistry() throws Exception {     KeyStoreParameters ksp = new KeyStoreParameters().     ksp.setResource("server.jks").     ksp.setPassword("password").     TrustManagersParameters tmp = new TrustManagersParameters().     tmp.setKeyStore(ksp).     SSLContextParameters sslContextParameters = new SSLContextParameters().     sslContextParameters.setSecureSocketProtocol("TLS").     sslContextParameters.setTrustManagers(tmp).     JndiRegistry registry = super.createRegistry().     registry.bind("sslContextParameters", sslContextParameters).     return registry. }
